## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="20373-256">O exemplo a seguir cria um <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> para o nó de serviços de domínio Active Directory.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="20373-256">The following example creates a <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry> for the node in the Active Directory Domain Services.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="20373-257">Em seguida, exibe o <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> e <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> propriedades de seus nós filho.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="20373-257">It then displays the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Name%2A> and <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectoryEntry.Path%2A> properties of its child nodes.</span></span>  
  
